#### [MODIFY] [docs/METRIC_DEFINITIONS.md](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/docs/METRIC_DEFINITIONS.md)
Add definitions for:
- `Sovereign Position (ECON_X, AUTH_Y)`: The actual policy-track record on the 11×11 grid.
- `Overton Center (OW_X, OW_Y)`: The faction-weighted ideological mean.
- `Ideological Tension (IT)`: `euclidean_distance(Position, OW_Center)` — measures how far the leader governs from the public's Overton Window.
- `Friction Coefficient (FC)`: A per-action constant (default 0.3) derived from the action's own ideological weight.
- `Flavor Label (FL)`: The human-readable political archetype at a given [(ECON_X, AUTH_Y)](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/src/chronos.rs#17-234) grid coordinate.

